<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Booking Confirmation - Evaga</title>

    <style>
      @import url("https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;600&display=swap");

      body {
        font-family: "Poppins", sans-serif;
        background-color: #f9f9f9;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 20px;
        text-align: center;
      }

      .email-container {
        max-width: 600px;
        background-color: #ffffff;
        padding: 20px;
        border-radius: 10px;
        box-shadow: 0px 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        margin: auto;
      }

      h2 {
        font-weight: 600;
        color: #333;
      }

      p {
        font-size: 16px;
        color: #555;
        line-height: 1.6;
      }

      ul {
        text-align: left;
        padding-left: 20px;
        margin: 10px 0;
      }

      li {
        font-size: 16px;
        margin-bottom: 8px;
      }

      strong {
        font-weight: 600;
      }

      .cta-button {
        display: inline-block;
        margin-top: 20px;
        padding: 12px 24px;
        font-size: 16px;
        color: #ffffff !important;
        background-color: #6a1b9a;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 5px;
        font-weight: 600;
      }

      .cta-button:hover {
        background-color: #4a0072;
      }

      .footer {
        font-size: 14px;
        color: #777;
        margin-top: 20px;
      }
    </style>
  </head>

  <body>
    <div class="email-container">
      <h2>🎉 Your Booking is Confirmed!</h2>
      <p>Hi <strong><%= customerName %></strong>,</p>
      <p>
        Great news! Your booking for <strong><%= vendorName %></strong> is confirmed. 🥳
      </p>
      <p><strong>📅 Event Details:</strong></p>
      <ul>
        <li>🔹 <strong>Service:</strong> <%= serviceName %></li>
        <li>🔹 <strong>Date & Time:</strong> <%= eventDate %> | <%= eventTime %></li>
        <li>🔹 <strong>Vendor Contact:</strong> <%= vendorContact %></li>
      </ul>
      <p><strong>💡 What’s Next?</strong></p>
      <ul>
        <li>● Connect with your vendor to finalize details</li>
        <li>● Check out our event planning tips for a hassle-free experience</li>
      </ul>
      <a
        href="<%= bookingDetailsUrl %>"
        class="cta-button"
        target="_blank"
        >📖 View Your Booking Details</a
      >
      <p class="footer">
        For any questions, feel free to reach out.<br />
        Happy Planning!<br />
        Team Evaga<br />
        📞 +91 8296157611 | 📧 <a href="mailto:info@evagaentertainment.com">info@evagaentertainment.com</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
